modName: Jupiter with ring and europa as moon and the moon all HI RES
summary: Jupiter with ring and europa as moon and the moon all HI RES
descriptionHtml:
Jupiter with his little known rings and the Europa moon...also added The moon our moon...IT\'S IMPORTANT TO INSTAL ALL FILES FROM THIS RAR TO Data/textures/sky
All phases have been added. The gap in the rings is the shadow of the Jupiter casted on the rings...so you can\'t see that part of the rings.

Use it with Moon size tweaker by akindain (http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=1037) if you want it to be big like in my screen shots.

OPTIONAL FILES
This is Jupiter without rings with several versions (I did it on the request):

default
hi contrast
hi contrast + saturation
hi contrast + saturation blue
Vibrance + saturation
Vibrance + saturation + contrast

I did all these variations because the texture does not correspond with the textures you get in the game...
NOTE: I use FXAA injector with saturation 0.7

Choose to your liking...
